  keywords  = {blood pressure measurement;blood pressure estimation;oscillometric pulse morphology;quantitative measures;arterial pressure;systolic pressure;diastolic pressure;Blood pressure;Biomedical monitoring;Morphology;Pulse measurements;Indexes;Pressure measurement;Silicon;Oscillometric waveform;Pulse morphology;Blood Pressure;Adult;Aged;Blood Pressure;Feasibility Studies;Female;Humans;Male;Middle Aged},
